### Dinneer API - Testes de Usuario
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiPath = /api/v1/usuario/UsuarioController

### ============================================
### 1. Listar todos os usuários
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}?operacao=getUsuarios

### ============================================
### 2. Buscar usuário por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}?operacao=getUsuario&id_usuario=1

### ============================================
### 3. Login de usuário (TESTE PRINCIPAL)
### Substitua com credenciais válidas do seu banco
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}?operacao=loginUsuario
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vl_email": "teste@email.com",
  "vl_senha": "senha123"
}

### ============================================
### 4. Criar novo usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}?operacao=createUsuario
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nu_cpf": "12345678900",
  "nm_usuario": "Teste",
  "nm_sobrenome": "Usuario",
  "vl_email": "teste@email.com",
  "vl_senha": "senha123",
  "vl_foto": null
}

### ============================================
### 5. Atualizar foto de perfil
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}?operacao=atualizarFotoPerfil
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_usuario": 1,
  "vl_foto": "https://exemplo.com/foto.jpg"
}

### ============================================
### 6. Deletar usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}?operacao=deleteUsuario
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_usuario": 999
}

### ============================================
### TESTE COM FORM DATA (alternativa ao JSON)
### Login usando application/x-www-form-urlencoded
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}?operacao=loginUsuario
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

vl_email=teste@email.com&vl_senha=senha123
